_sText:
Well, this is Fy_glassdawn ... one of my first CSS maps.

Due to the fact that this map is Fy, you do NOT have a buy zone. Thats what the weapons spread around the map are for.

Features:

   - 2 Separate Spawn rooms both with a small amount of water for the player's safety after jumping from the Glass platform.

   - All Glass on this map is breakable, so be careful when going up there for the AWPs.

   - 2 Weapon rooms ( Mp5 one and an UMP45 both also having snipers)

   - Water containing 4 flash and 4 explosive grenades

   - Other weapons include deagle, para. m4a1 and ak47.

   - Map supports 32 people.
